sols:
$\begin{bmatrix}
a_{0}\\b_{0}
\\c_{0}

\end{bmatrix}
\rightarrow \begin{bmatrix}
a_{n}\\b_{n}
\\ c_{n}

\end{bmatrix}$

as \emph{n} approaches infinity. If the solution starts as a steady
state solution then it will not change with n. ie. we need to find a
steady state solution.

One solution is:

$\begin{bmatrix}
a_{0}\\b_{0}
\\c_{0}

\end{bmatrix} = \begin{bmatrix}
13/41\\9/41
\\19/41

\end{bmatrix}$
